block vars
  - var activeLink = 'vue';
  - var title = 'Tabs Vue Component | Framework7 Vue Documentation';

block content

    .docs-nav
      include ../_docs-vue-menu
    .docs-content
      h1 Tabs Vue Component
      p Tabs allow to simply switch between different content. Tabs Vue component represents <a href="../docs/tabs.html">Tabs</a> component.
      h2 Examples
      pre
        code
          :code
            <f7-tabs>
              <f7-tab id="tab1" active>Tab 1 content...</f7-tab>
              <f7-tab id="tab2">Tab 2 content...</f7-tab>
            </f7-tabs>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="tabs">
              <div id="tab1" class="tab acitive">Tab 1 content...</div>
              <div id="tab2" class="tab">Tab 2 content...</div>
            </div>
      h4 Animated tabs
      pre
        code
          :code
            <f7-tabs animated>
              <f7-tab id="tab1" active>Tab 1 content...</f7-tab>
              <f7-tab id="tab2">Tab 2 content...</f7-tab>
            </f7-tabs>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="tabs-animated-wrap">
              <div class="tabs">
                <div id="tab1" class="tab acitive">Tab 1 content...</div>
                <div id="tab2" class="tab">Tab 2 content...</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            </div>
      h4 Swipeable tabs
      pre
        code
          :code
            <f7-tabs swipeable>
              <f7-tab id="tab1" active>Tab 1 content...</f7-tab>
              <f7-tab id="tab2">Tab 2 content...</f7-tab>
            </f7-tabs>
      p Renders to:
      pre
        code
          :code
            <div class="tabs-swipeable-wrap">
              <div class="tabs">
                <div id="tab1" class="tab acitive">Tab 1 content...</div>
                <div id="tab2" class="tab">Tab 2 content...</div>
              </div>
            </div>
      h2 Properties
      table.params-table
        thead
          tr
            th Prop
            th Type
            th Description
        tbody
          tr
            th(colspan="3") &lt;f7-tabs&gt; properties
          tr
            td animated
            td boolean
            td Enables animated tabs
          tr
            td swipeable
            td boolean
            td Enables swipeable tabs
          tr
            th(colspan="3") &lt;f7-tab&gt; properties
          tr
            td active
            td boolean
            td Defines currently active/visible tab
      h2 Tab Methods
      table.methods-table
        tr
          td .show(<span>animated</span>)
          td Show tab
      h2 Tab Events
      table.events-table
        thead
          tr
            th Event
            th Description
        tbody
          tr
            td tab:show
            td Event will be triggered when Tab becomes visible/active
          tr
            td tab:hide
            td Event will be triggered when Tab becomes invisible/inactive
      h2 Switch Tabs
      p You can control/switch tabs:
      ul
        li by clicking on <a href="button.html">Button</a> or <a href="link.html">Link</a> specifying related tab's ID using <code>tab-link</code> prop
        li using its <a href="../docs/tabs.html#show-tab-using-javascript">JavaScript API</a>
        li using <a href="navigation-router.html#nested-routes">Tab Routes</a>